					<div class="map-iframe m1024">{{ map_1024 | raw}}</div>
					<div class="map-iframe m1440">{{ map_1440 | raw}}</div>
					<div class="map-iframe m1920">{{ map_1440 | raw}}</div>
					<div class="map-iframe m2560">{{ map_1440 | raw}}</div>
					<div class="info">
						<ul class="address">
							<li class="part addr">
								<h4>Addres 1</h4>
								<p>
									{{ contact_address_short1 }}
									<br>
									{{ contact_address_state }} {{ contact_zip1 }}
								</p>
							</li>
							<li class="part addr">
								<h4>Addres 2</h4>
								<p>
									{{ contact_address_short2 }}
									<br>
									{{ contact_district2 }}, {{ contact_address_state }} {{ contact_zip2 }}
								</p>
							</li>
							<div class="part phone">
								<h4>Contact</h4>
								<p>
									Phone: {{ contact_phone }}
									<br>
									Fax: {{ contact_fax }}
									<br>
									<a href="mailto:{{ contact_email1 }}?subject=From Contacts Page">{{ contact_email1 }}</a>
								</p>
							</div>
						</ul>
						<div class="form">
							{% include "AppBundle:Contact:contact_block_form.html.twig" %}
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

    <section id="about">
			<div class="container">
			  <div class="row row-eq-height">
			    <div class="liberty">
						<img id="sl" src="/img/sl.png" alt="Sharova Law Firm">
			    </div>
					<div class="why-us">
						<h3>{{ whyUsBlockContacts.name  | replace({" Contacts":""})}}</h3>
            {{ whyUsBlockContacts.content | raw }}
            <div class="text-containter">
              <p>Knowledge without passion can be considered a recital of facts at best.</p>
              <p>You don’t want a lawyer going to court with you, fighting for you, while just reciting the
                  facts. You need a passionate fighter who is willing to put the work in, who can empathize
                  with you. You also need a team of attorneys that do know the facts and are willing to
                  uncover them to preserve their client’s rights and lives. The attorneys at the Law Office of
                  Yelena Sharova P.C. are the attorneys you are looking for, whether it is a criminal, civil
                  or family matter; these defense attorneys are the cream of the crop. Call for a Free
                  15-minute Consultation and see why hiring the Law Office of Yelena Sharova is right for you.
                  Don’t put your life on hold.</p>
							<h3>CALL TODAY!</h3>
							<hr>
            </div>
						{% include "default/fb.html.twig" %}
						</div>
					</div>
			  </div>
			</div>
		</section>
  </wrapper>
